## 22. Format export `.artcb`

Fichier ZIP contenant :

```
export.artcb (ZIP)
├── manifest.json       # version, date, graph_id, chain_length
├── graph.json          # IR complet
├── chain.jsonl         # Blocs blockchain exportés
├── rtleg.jsonl         # Événements RT-LEG
├── vectors.faiss       # Index vectoriel (optionnel)
└── checksum.sha256     # Hash global
```

**manifest.json :**

```json
{
  "format": "artcb-export",
  "version": "0.1",
  "exported_at": "2026-07-04T20:00:00Z",
  "graph_id": "uuid",
  "node_count": 42,
  "block_count": 7,
  "pol_score": 0.81,
  "reversible": true
}
```

